high_descs: Turn around, go forward, hang a right, go to the counter between the fridge and stove.
Pick up the yellow handled knife that is on the counter.
Turn to the right, go to the counter on the other side of the stove where the bread is.
Cut the bread into slices.
Put the knife down on the counter with the bread.
Pick up a slice of bread from the counter.
Turn to the left, go to the fridge that is ahead on the right.
Put the bread inside the fridge and close the door, remove the bread from the fridge once it is cold.
Turn to the right, go to the stove, hang a right, go to the microwave that is above the sink.
Put the bread inside the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put cold bread inside the microwave.

high_descs: Turn to your left then head to stove counter on your left
Pick up the knife at the right beside the tomato
Turn right then head to the other side of stove counter
Slice the bread on the counter
Put the knife on the counter in front of the bread
Pick up the slice of  bread
Turn left the towards the fridge
Open the fridge then put it the slice of bread then take it out
Turn right then head to the microwave
Open the microwave put in the slice of bread and close the microwave
anns.task_desc: Put the chilled slice bread to the microwave

pick up the sharp knife with the yellow handle from the counter
turn right and move to the counter that is on the right side of the stove, turn left to face the counter
slice the loaf of bread that is on the counter with the knife
put the knife on to the counter
pick up the end slice of bread from the counter
turn to the left moving passed the stove and stop at the fridge on the right, turn to face the fridge
open the fridge door, put the slice of bread on to the middle shelf, close the door for five seconds, open the door, remove the slice of bread and close the door
turn to the right and move forwards, at the stove on the left, turn to the right and move to the sink
put the slice of bread in to the microwave that is above the sink
